snippet.title: Mirrors of Epiphany - Gameplay trailer #1
snippet.description:
Mirrors of Epiphany is the upcoming, second game from creator of logic gate puzzler Pure Logic. A free demo, including the 10 first puzzles, is available here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2643000/Mirrors_of_Epiphany/

Wishlist (on Steam) to be notified when the full game is released 👍

Follow to get the latest news:
https://store.steampowered.com/developer/sigmundhoien
https://x.com/SigmundHoien
